                        In this project, we focused on applying advanced artificial intelligence and computational methods 
                        to solve complex problems in medical diagnostics and biomedical engineering. We utilized various 
                        machine learning models, particularly Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), to analyze diverse 
                        medical imagery. Our research demonstrated the use of AI for diagnosing COVID-19 from lung X-rays, 
                        segmenting brain lesions and breast tumors from MRIs and ultrasound, and diagnosing biomechanical 
